Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.12,0:23:51.66,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:57.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直尋找著
